{"tid":1684783,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"負資產出現了！","createTime":"2019-10-31T09:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T04:29:11.000Z","uid":62393,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1875299c813bfdb2f41e0e81dbb7fd662f938e23","tid":1684783,"uid":62393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"金管局公布，截至今年第三季，負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數由今年第二季末的1宗，大幅增加至第三季末的53宗，相關個案大部分為銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款，少數涉及按揭保險計劃的貸款。<br />\n<br />\n該局指，負資產住宅按揭貸款涉及的金額由第二季末的300萬元，增加109倍至第三季末的3.3億元。負資產住宅按揭貸款中無抵押部分的金額升至第三季末的700萬元，第二季為12萬元。銀行自從2011年第一季，並無錄得任何拖欠三個月以上的負資產住宅按揭貸款紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：明報<br />\n<br />\n【負資產】本港第3季末負資產宗數急升至53宗"},{"pid":"52ab8b9999723f3a347ec8d5d1cda11c08319801","tid":1684783,"uid":54884,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T09:30:02.000Z","msg":"過千宗先算"},{"pid":"5accc1e638d51b089cff8e786e0b3a5682357885","tid":1684783,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"9成按之後冇升咩 竟然多咗負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25d56c30fb34ba3212e24fe9141edc0dcc96f68","tid":1684783,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"比第二季多五千幾%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b059e6791b1cee8c6b2af3e76e648090ff19b96","tid":1684783,"uid":44783,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5accc1e638d51b089cff8e786e0b3a5682357885","tid":1684783,"uid":8880,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"9成按之後冇升咩 竟然多咗負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢個數據去到9月30<br />\n9成按之後果53個業主如果未跳樓應該變返正資產"},{"pid":"9bbb91356225e1f05082c6791275c80006d9b1ba","tid":1684783,"uid":122377,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"樓跌1-2% 已經50幾宗負資產 <img src=\"/assets/faces/